        "# 🏆 **Capstone: Build a Parliament Simulation**\n",
        "\n",
        "Now let's combine everything: classes, attributes, methods, inheritance, and composition. You will build a Parliament that can hold a vote on a proposition.\n",
        "\n",
        "Here's the system you will construct step by step:\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "Party  ──(has-a)──▶  Politician  ──(is-a)──▶  President\n",
        "                         │\n",
        "                    (has-many)\n",
        "                         │\n",
        "                    Parliament\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "The `Party`, `Politician`, and `President` classes from the demos above are your starting point. Now you need to build `Parliament`.\n"
      ]
