        "- Add them all to a `Parliament` with a specific proposition\n",
        "- Hold the vote and attempt to pass the law\n",
        "- Print the result\n",
        "\n",
        "**⭐ Extra:** Add a `__str__()` method to `Parliament` that prints a summary: the proposition, member count, and vote result.\n"
